WEBVTT

00:04:28.958 --> 00:04:30.476
in a single frame.

00:04:30.500 --> 00:04:33.875
(Speaks Spanish)

00:04:44.417 --> 00:04:48.184
A cartoon needs to communicate
the core of a story with its precision.

00:04:48.208 --> 00:04:49.476
And when it succeeds,

00:04:49.500 --> 00:04:52.643
its message can have the effect
of inoculating people

00:04:52.667 --> 00:04:54.542
with a dose of skepticism.

00:04:54.958 --> 00:04:58.000
(Speaks Spanish)